snippet.title: 东方远空界 ~ Ultimate Vitality of Imagination: ReimuA Lunatic 1CC + TLB (Alternative Route)
snippet.description:
Good fangame, even more impressive when you learn that it's all made by pretty much a single person.

I managed to get all the gems in this run, honestly didn't expect that.
Yuck, nearly capped the TLB spell :pensive:
There's also a small recording hiccup in stage 3, apparently my video card decided to screw off to Mars for a second there. I didn't want to re-record it, so whatever.

Get the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1700220/__Ultimate_Vitality_of_Imagination/
